comment.body:
Method updates the passed ComponentInfo object in the database to the values of the passed object. The method does not change any properties of the component.

@param pComponentInfo ComponentInfo object whose data should be used to update the ComponentInfo in the database. The passed ComponentInfo has to be retrieved using the Service's Method <code>getComponentInfo(...)</code>. The parameter must not be null and must have a valid service object id.
@return ComponentInfo object describing the updated object in the database. This object is not the same as the one that was passed to the method. The passed ComponentInfo object should not be used any longer since its data was not updated. The method never returns null.
